{"word":"ἀπαιδευσία","slug":"ἀπαιδευσία","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἀπαιδευσία</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b>from <a href='S:ἀπαίδευτος'><el>ἀπαίδευτος</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>want of education</i>, <b><a href='S:Thucydides'>Thuc.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Plato'>Plat.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><i>ignorance, boorishness, coarseness</i>, <b><a href='S:Plato'>Plat.</a></b>, <a href='S:et cetera'>etc.</a><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:genitive'>gen.</a>, <el>ἀπαιδευσίαι ὀργῆς</el> <i>from want of control over</i> passion, <b><a href='S:Thucydides'>Thuc.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}